<td style="border-top: 1px solid #AAA; text-align: center; width: 25%;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/icon-documents/alet.png" alt="alet.png" class="image" /></td>
</tr>
</table>
<hr />
<p><strong>RISKS AND DRAWBACKS:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Repeated uses of Aletheia glyphs have shown to increase cases of dissociation, migraines and seizures.</li>
<li>The current generation of Aletheia glyphs have limited information capacity.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>ADDITIONAL NOTES</strong>: Project Aletheia's primary use case has been superseded by modern mnestics and has been placed on indefinite hold.</p>
